headline: Fortune Media and Great Place To Work Name Cadence to "100 Best Companies to Work For" in 2025, Ranking No. 11
summary: SAN JOSE, Calif., April 02, 2025--Great Place To Work and Fortune magazine recognized Cadence as one of the Fortune 100 Best Companies to Work For in 2025, securing the 11th position.
